ratio of\nH$\\alpha$/[OIII] within the redshift range of $0<z<3$. Our results show the\nknown trend of increasing H$\\alpha$/[O III] flux ratio with H$\\alpha$ flux at\nlow redshift, which becomes a weaker trend at higher redshifts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Jul 2019 03:43:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Oct 2019 21:32:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-28"}
