ible\nthat solar extreme UV intensity and cosmic-ray variations influenced the\nobserved albedo trends. The albedo variations might also be linked with\ntemporal variations of the upper cloud SO2 gas abundance, which affects the\nH2SO4-H2O aerosol formation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Jul 2019 03:57:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-04"}
