an be engineered in a\nsimilar way to form a class of ferroelectrics, in which MPB solid solutions are\nalso included, that we propose to coin as transitional ferroelectrics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Jul 2019 06:05:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-29"}
