umber of servers k, the ratio between m_c and m_s, the\ninverse of the augmentation factor 1/\\delta and the competitive ratio of the\nsimulated k-Page Migration algorithm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Jul 2019 12:07:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-24"}
